1153
00:41:47.464 --> 00:41:51.009 position:21.43%,start align:start size:65.24% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>we'll send down an away team.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1154
00:41:52.844 --> 00:41:55.263 position:38.57%,start align:start size:30.95% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>(</c.mono_sans></c.white><c.white><c.mono_sans><i> sighing</i></c.mono_sans></c.white><c.white><c.mono_sans> )</c.mono_sans></c.white>

