00:41:59.892 --> 00:42:02.645 position:40.48%,start align:start size:27.14% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>you need.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1160
00:42:02.645 --> 00:42:06.274 position:23.33%,start align:start size:63.33% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to offer as much as you did.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1161
00:42:02.645 --> 00:42:06.274 position:32.86%,start align:start size:42.38% line:79.29% 
